 | single             = 1. [[The Girl Is Mine]]<br />2. [[Billie Jean]]<br />3. [[Beat It]]<br />4. [[Wanna Be Startin' Somethin']]<br />5. [[Human Nature (Michael Jackson)|Human Nature]]<br />6. [[P.Y.T. (Pretty Young Thing)]]<br />7. [[Thriller (chanson)|Thriller]]
